snippet.title: Cemetery of Bob Trailer
snippet.description:
Cemetery of Bob is a challenging roguelike auto-battler focused on tactical aspect of gameplay. Build an army of the undead. Recruit your zombies, upgrade your skeletons, observe your enemy and adapt to his strategy. Do everything in your power to defend the Cemetery from Bob's usurpation.

You can play demo in your browser here 🧟 https://jokerddzz.itch.io/cemetery-of-bob
Wishlist here 👉 https://store.steampowered.com/app/2813240/Cemetery_of_Bob/
Discord 👩‍💻 https://discord.gg/FqSef679pM
